


obsv_mat(1)                    Scilab Function                    obsv_mat(1)






NAME
  obsv_mat - observability matrix

CALLING SEQUENCE
  [O]=obsv_mat(A,C)
  [O]=obsv_mat(sl)

PARAMETERS

  A,C,O     : matrices

  sl        : syslin list

DESCRIPTION
  obsv_mat returns the observability matrix
  O=[C; CA; CA^2;...; CA^(n-1) ]

SEE ALSO
  contrss, obsvss, obs_gram





































